results.deck:
EA Tiburon is an internal development team of EA. They are the yearly developers of sports series like the Madden, NCAA Football, Tiger Woods PGA Tour and Nascar series. This team is currently located in Orlando, Florida.
T
results.description:
Overview

Tiburon recently worked on a new NBA Jam game and in a November 3, 2010 investor call, it was confirmed that Tiburon would also take over development of the NBA Elite franchise.

Tiburon Studios was purchased by EA in 1998 and renamed EA Tiburon.
